# 🛡️ 3. Focus on Defense First

Beginners usually lose because they attack too much.

Better strategy:
- Block attacks  
- Wait for opening  
- Counter attack smartly  

---

# 🔥 4. Don’t Spam Attacks

Random tapping reduces your chances of winning.

Instead:
- Time your hits  
- Use combos carefully  
- Maintain distance control  

---

# 💰 5. Upgrade Strategy Matters

Don’t waste coins on random upgrades.

Focus on:
- Main weapon upgrades  
- Armor improvements  
- Useful skills only  

